 "blurb": "Restoration Shaman is TBC's raid-healing multiplier: Chain Heal hits three targets per cast and Earth Shield frees a tank healer's globals, while Mana Tide bails out the whole group's healers. The phase lists below are Chain-Heal-first — bounce healing scales harder with +healing than any single-target spell. This Phase 1 snapshot aggregates 402 top healing parses from Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon; the highest-consensus pick is Totem of Healing Rains at 75% usage.",
